'''Nal Raka Space''' was a large portion of the [[Naboo system/Legends|Naboo system]] and surrounding [[Star system/Legends|star system]] under control of the [[Nal Raka Criminal Empire]].

==History==
[[Borvo]]'s pilots swarmed the area, and would kill all [[Royal Naboo Security Forces/Legends|Royal Naboo Security Forces]] pilots that entered.

